@startuml
!theme plain
autonumber

actor "Logistics Operator" as Operator
participant "User Interface\n(UI)" as UI
participant "Backend Service\n(Port System)" as Backend

Operator -> UI : 1: create or update Resource
activate UI
UI -> Backend : 1.1: Request (CreateResource / UpdateResource)
activate Backend
Backend --> UI : 1.2: Response (ResourceDto)
deactivate Backend
UI --> Operator : 1.3: Display confirmation
deactivate UI

@enduml